e:T79a,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Phrase (Memsource) better than Translated?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Phrase (Memsource) scores 8.0 overall while Translated scores 7.0. Phrase (Memsource) is best for localization teams and translation agencies, while Translated excels for businesses and marketing teams."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Phrase (Memsource) or Translated?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Phrase (Memsource) starts at $25/mo and Translated starts at $0.08/word.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Phrase (Memsource) to Translated?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Phrase (Memsource) and Translated support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Phrase (Memsource) vs Translated?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Phrase (Memsource) holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10. Translated has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise Phrase (Memsource) for comprehensive tms with strong cat tools and Translated for high-quality professional translations."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Phrase (Memsource) or Translated?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Phrase (Memsource) for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Translated remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize high-quality professional translations. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+j